#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:142
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Sniper Girl wastes no time hailing you. \"They just keep coming, with better equipment every time, to rob us. I just can't catch a breath. I know that's why you're here too...\" You're about to say something to cheer her up when she cuts you off. \"Because there's NO better shop in this universe for Stealth gear! So efficient, pirates dream about it, coalitions plot to acquire it, and renegades jump in to steal it! Buy while you still can!\n"
"\t\tDid you know your Cloaking loses 20% of its maximum duration when most weapons start firing?\".\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tTurns out she's still in character. RK sector professionals must have seen some shit, you think to yourself.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\"...And for your timely assistance, here's a little incentive to buy.\" You realize the gift is your \"Thank you\", and shrug.\n"
"\t\tThen you take one look at the wares and immediately understand why the attacker came here.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\"Oh and, some of this stuff is so hard to source it shouldn't even exist, so only 1 purchase per customer. But for you I'll make it 3.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:156
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright then."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:180
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_RKS_FIGHT_LEAD_TITANS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Right after jumping in, you notice an imposing Shell ship jumping away, leaving behind a few crates and a message for you: \"Run while you can! Deathhhh is hhhere, we only got away with our lives thhhanks to smart hhhhacking!\"\n"
"\t\tThe only other ship here is a small RadiKal Bam dropship collecting the crates in a hurry, but now that they've noticed you it seems like they're moving to attack!\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tYou tell them you're not here to mess with them. The captain who answers definitely looks abnormally big for its race.\n"
"\t\t\"Yes, miss or mister Renegade. Nobody's flying around this godforsaken nebula all day, but you just happened to get here during this short skirmish, right?\n"
"\t\tWell I am not taking the risk to believe that, and if it was somehow the truth, blame your own bad luck!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tUnless you have escape tools or something very convincing to tell them, it seems you'll have to fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:198
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_RKS_FIGHT_LEAD_TITANS\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_rk_defromorius\"]/text"
