msgstr ""
"\"--NEW OBJECTIVE: DEFUSE SITUATION-- Stop. Greetings.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\"Oh shit they've captured Defromorius! DIE SCU-\" Somebody on the other ship interrupts the captain before he starts firing. \"Don't be an idiot, calm down and look again\" \"What? Wait. Oh. Oh! Sorry sir, I should really chill every now and then to avoid making mistakes like this. Here's an apology, see you around sir!\" Without missing a beat they turn to their second-in-command. \"Find the bastards!\""

