#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:849
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"NEBULA_RKS_HIDEOUT_UNLOCK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Looks like the RadiKals really do work with (or for) eldritch beings... Your mind becomes foggy as a disembodied voice starts resonating inside your skull.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\"I know what you need, Renegade. This beacon so nicely hidden in the nebula could become your very own hideout. Accessible across different timelines thanks to my power.\n"
"\t\tShow me that you deserve it by killing one of the current residents and razing their settlement to the ground, hahe!\n"
"\t\tAre you just going to sit there letting other Renegades get stronger? You know they will inevitably end up at the same beacon as you some day, and that will surely be the last resting place for one of you.\n"
"\t\tDon't you wish to make sure you will be the one making it out alive? CHOOSE.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tThat last word carried the weight of sin, in the form of both guilt and regret. You need only bear one of those."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:862
