msgstr ""
"You barely even reach the Jump button as a small Shell fleet jumps in! A very angry Radiant ship immediately hails you.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\"Federation simpletons, don't get me wrong, these guys actually do cool science, and we even know a few of our rogue elites are high-ranking in there.\"\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tFor a brief moment, you think this is gonna end peacefully.\n"
"\t\t\n"
