"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrive at a red planet with volcanoes so large you can see them from orbit, and around them, a multitude of structures that look like giant insects. The atmosphere looks like it's on fire.\n"
"\t\tTaking a closer look, you notice that many of the \"structures\" actually move, sampling lava, putting things in it, and doing all sorts of strange experiments.\n"
"\t\tYou can also tell that there are many scientific facilities, factories and even what looks like stadiums all over the surface, a good distance away from the lava flows.\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\tSomeone on the planet is hailing you. \"We see you, Federation Renegade. If you have reason to be here, now's time to show proof.\""

